name: FaceA赛博女友
description:
这是一个完全由Ai生成的虚拟女友，原始人物是过去一年用Artbreeder数次迭代生成的个人向DreamGirl，中间经faceplay生成真人向图片和视频并筛选出来的训练集，整个过程不涉及任何现实中的人物安全无公害。

在不同工具和平台的转换后最终的训练集与一开始artbreeder生成的形象有了一定偏移，在后续的版本中我将继续改进使她更符合个人审美取向。

基于ChilloutMix训练，majicMIX上表现也不错。

推荐权重0.4-0.8

由于中间过程产生的素材美颜严重，导致训练集人物眼睛比真实人类眼睛大一些，不过都赛博创生了诸位道友应该也不太在意这些。

This is a fully AI-generated virtual girlfriend, the original character is a person-oriented DreamGirl who has been working with Artbreeder in multiple iterations over the last year, with an intervening training set generated by faceplay that generates real human-oriented images and videos and filters out the training set, the whole process is completely non-technical and somewhat biased without involving any real humans safely and harmlessly.

Based on ChilloutMix training, majicMIX also performed well.

Recommendation weight 0.4-0.8

Due to the intermediary process by the material produced beauty serious, resulting in the training set character eyes than the real human eyes are a little larger, but are Cybertronics you guys should not worry too much about this.
